    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> April 21. 1774.</dateline>
                <opener>
                    <salute>My Lord</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I shall think myself very happy if (<hi rend="underline">This Time</hi>) I shall
                    be able to do justice to the Beauty of <placeName ref="pl0821">your grace's
                        places</placeName>.<note type="editorial">See Pennant's letters to the 3<hi rend="superscript">rd</hi> Duke of Atholl on 20<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> December 1771 and 27<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> August
                        1774.</note> but as I am also sollicitous about accuracy; I take The liberty
                    to request a full history of <placeName ref="pl0110">the castle of
                        Blair</placeName>, in foundation &amp; the various greater events that have
                    befell it. I shall be most extremely happy if your Grace would direct that such
                    an account be drawn up in a brief manner &amp; transtmitted to me by post to
                        <placeName ref="pl0001">Downing Flintshire</placeName>, with convenient
                    speed.</p>
                <p>I beg my respectfull compliments to <persName ref="pe0577">the
                        Dutchess</persName>; &amp; am with great esteem, my Lord</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Your Grace's <lb/>obliged &amp; most obedient <lb/>humble Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232">Thomas
                            Pennant</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>I think this summer to visit <placeName ref="pl0707">y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Graces's Kingdom of Man</placeName>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <handShift/>from M<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi>
                    <persName ref="pe0232">Penant</persName>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> April 21<hi rend="superscript">st.</hi>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="underline">1771</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
